text.tspan: POI Properties which could be encoded in a Map Marker
- Level (1,2,3) - Level 2 is particularly broad ranging
- Power (KW) - Many POIs do not have this
- Charging Speed - A generic indication of speed/power
- Access (Public, Private, Paid, Membership Required etc)
- Presence of Photos etc for POI
